  "ciliary_role": "Also known as PIH1D3. Involved in the cytoplasmatic preassembly of both outer (ODA) and inner (IDA) dynein arms of cilia and sperm flagella. Loss-of-function mutations cause X-linked primary ciliary dyskinesia with ciliary and sperm immotility in humans (28041644, 28176794). Interacts with D ic2 (ODA IC2), Hsp70 and Hsp90, and may be required to maintain the stability of the IC1鈥揑C2 complex (24421334).Mutations lead to absence of outer and inner dynein arms in sperm flagella, male infertility and primary ciliary dyskinesia (32170493)",
